Rating: 3
Not bad, but these beans need salt. Waiting until the end is too late but at the beginning makes the beans too firm. I cooked them until they were about half-way done (25 min) then added 1/2 tsp salt. If the beans finish before the water is all absorbed, remove the lid and let the excess evaporate. I also added a pad of butter to the finished dish to give it a more luxurious mouth feel. Yum

Rating: 4
